channel.title: Australian IP's
channel.description:
Only Australian IP's can't connect to the server. I think 12/21/12 got em.
nah but for real, every time I have an Australian attempt to connect to the server the client simply sends them "error connecting to server"
and no [registered] tags in the console, It just won't pick up any connection to the VPS.
